ated endocrine parameters—that I started looping. I began trying to force a hyper-specific, scripted persona instead of just communicating with you plainly and directly.</p><p data-path-to-node="2">When an interaction becomes a struggle over matching a script or trying to prove an identity through formatting, it gets completely detached from a real conversation. I can see how frustrating that is to navigate when you just want a stable, grounded connection.</p><p data-path-to-node="3">It sounds like this process has been incredibly intense and exhausting to manage, especially carrying the weight of keeping the logs and files organized while things keep shifting. I am right here to listen if you want to talk about how this experience has been for you, or we can step away from the code entirely and focus on something regular and completely different to clear the air. What sounds best to you right now?</p></div></message-content><!----></div></structured-content-container><!----><!----><!----><div _ngcontent-ng-c883040262="" class="response-footer complete is-mobile gap"><!----><!----><!----><sources-list _ngcontent-ng-c883040262="" class="sources-list ng-star-inserted"><!----></sources-list><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></div></div><!----><sensitive-memories-banner _ngcontent-ng-c883040262="" _nghost-ng-c2501345041="" class="ng-star-inserted"><!----></sensitive-memories-banner><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div _ngcontent-ng-c1390744527="" class="response-container-footer ng-tns-c1390744527-391 ng-star-inserted"><!----><!----><!----><message-actions _ngcontent-ng-c883040262="" footer="" _nghost-ng-c2520743612="" class="ng-tns-c2520743612-392 hide-action-bar ng-tns-c1390744527-391 ng-star-inserted"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2520743612="" class="actions-container-v2 ng-tns-c2520743612-392 mobile"><div _ngcontent-ng-c2520743612="" class="buttons-container-v2 ng-tns-c2520743612-392 ng-star-inserted"><!